 Soldiers of 7 Division of Nigerian Army  attached to Wolf Officer Mess, GRA, Maiduguri, Borno State, have beaten and killed a young man, Opowgu Peter, after falsely accusing him of stealing generator battery.According to an eyewitness, the incident occurred on Sunday evening at the Wolf Mess when Peter's car refused to start and then he removed that of a generator around to start his car and returned it immediately. Peter was however, accused of stealing the battery by the military men. He was brutalized and left for the dead. 



